{"tid":553224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際報告指「普教中」學生閱讀力較低分　楊潤雄：無關教學語言","createTime":"2018-02-07T08:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T09:57:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5d7524a9a01ae4d5eac7acd6502f87dcee416a66","tid":553224,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180207/s00001/5907ededb2975570ca2d0b4e8d2af0eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180207%2Fs00001%2F5907ededb2975570ca2d0b4e8d2af0eb.jpg&h=55ae47f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際教育成績評估協會「全球學生閱讀能力進展研究」顯示，「普教中（普通話教授中文）」學生閱讀平均分，較非「普教中」學生低。教育局長楊潤雄認為，學生閱讀表現與學校是否採用普通話作為教學語言，沒有明顯關連。<br />\n<br />\n2016年「全球學生閱讀能力進展研究」，調查全港139間小學、超過3,000名小四學生，發現學校以普通話作授課語言的學生，閱讀平均分比非普通話授課學生低，反映「普教中」不代表可以提升學生閱讀能力。<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民鄭松泰在立法會大會，問教育局會否檢討「普教中」遠程目標。教育局長楊潤雄書面回覆，無論「普教中」或「廣教中（廣東話教中文）」，均能提升學生中文閱讀能力，認為學生閱讀表現，與學校是否採用普通話作為中文教學語言，無明顯關連。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄表示，教育局會繼續在教授中文方面，向學校提供協助、專業培訓等。<br />\n<br />\n他另提到，語常會2008/2009學年推出為期6年、協助中小學推行「普教中」計劃；最近5年，有40所中小學參與計劃（2013/2014學年為計劃最後一年），相關開支約1,400萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180207/s00001/1517990346438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180207%2Fs00001%2F1517990346438&d=VDmOLWg1ojZGYHKK%2FvrRCpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c9a9013f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180207%2Fs00001%2F1517990346438&h=32adccd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180207/s00001/1517990346438</a>"},{"pid":"0ed9d0f5606d5bb8af11435c170502e034ac6a65","tid":553224,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:51:47.000Z","msg":"今次呢個幾時死老母"},{"pid":"37df6de79ed30adb02dc1a9b86f567f3599cb7d6","tid":553224,"uid":59898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都仲有得拗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e55cb51ea9cfe3d580f8a248a22e357753fe26a","tid":553224,"uid":25424,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"教育局長楊潤雄書面回覆，無論「普教中」或「廣教中（廣東話教中文）」，均能提升學生中文閱讀能力<br />\n<br />\n原來一開始鳩吹會有改善，但依家咁講即屎忽痕做樣無分別既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔講政治任務都無人信啦"},{"pid":"2babd3efaf990f1adf3c4745fe089fd01d99dda3","tid":553224,"uid":38671,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:58:44.000Z","msg":"點會無影響<br />\n細細個老師已經教廣東話同書面語<br />\n但而家係無教學生分北京話同書面語"},{"pid":"a0b4cecfd8de155c6fd36854521e89124e96d837","tid":553224,"uid":8308,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:59:53.000Z","msg":"既然一樣，咁仲要普教中黎做咩？"},{"pid":"d5136db0c1d9718e353c5afa8f1953aa8dd539af","tid":553224,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a0b4cecfd8de155c6fd36854521e89124e96d837","tid":553224,"uid":8308,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:59:53.000Z","msg":"既然一樣，咁仲要普教中黎做咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:02:10.000Z","msg":"所以唯一結論係：<br />\n<br />\n「普教中」真正目的係消滅粵文化"},{"pid":"942ee0302e239272b89ba50d8ae97c3d9da1f08f","tid":553224,"uid":38671,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3e55cb51ea9cfe3d580f8a248a22e357753fe26a","tid":553224,"uid":25424,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"教育局長楊潤雄書面回覆，無論「普教中」或「廣教中（廣東話教中文）」，均能提升學生中文閱讀能力<br />\n<br />\n原來一開始鳩吹會有改善，但依家咁講即屎忽痕做樣無分別既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔講政治任務都無人信啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"鬼拍後尾枕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129877baaba9e3bbfc815cff08755dac76412470","tid":553224,"uid":34023,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:03:52.000Z","msg":"教育局長楊潤雄認為，學生閱讀表現與學校是否採用普通話作為教學語言，沒有明顯關連。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有明顯關係係就仆咗街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n普教中同非普教中都有助提升閱讀表現，屌你有擺時間落去就點都會提升嫁啦，依家講緊邊樣有效啲，如果證明唔到普教中更有效咁你班弱智政府官即係鳩做啦<br />\n<br />\n浪費納稅人金錢呀你地班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"749d9578c212cefc562048a871f396fb04ad17be","tid":553224,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:05:13.000Z","msg":"依家超過一半中小學用普教中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcadedb54e52e356ca947e6ea9e890716edd9b38","tid":553224,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"749d9578c212cefc562048a871f396fb04ad17be","tid":553224,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:05:13.000Z","msg":"依家超過一半中小學用普教中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:17:54.000Z","msg":"港語學好似話 &gt; 60%<br />\n十分大鑊<br />\n<br />\n班教畜係精英班用蝗語教<br />\n<br />\n搞到班細路以為蝗語係高等語言<br />\n<br />\n好CLS"},{"pid":"796dc2864c295c5c96dd3c9df7a889d4ce6f1b98","tid":553224,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.facebook.com/antileftplastic/photos/a.1504471819803215.1073741828.1504351596481904/1691475087769553/?type=3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fantileftplastic%2Fphotos%2Fa.1504471819803215.1073741828.1504351596481904%2F1691475087769553%2F%3Ftype%3D3&h=513de9d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"874c967e6722c3c97be99b5a6847c47ae71ea609","tid":553224,"uid":92353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:30:52.000Z","msg":"殖民統治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64129d120e449da637bda14bcb6c3d6ae1969f3c","tid":553224,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:38:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「不要普教中」</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7b36b53e2009eb6bc2122f7ae99976f9b16055c3","tid":553224,"uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:55:47.000Z","msg":"根本就係政治任務黎<br />\n<br />\n要推就話我手寫我口 到有結果出黎就話同教學言語無關係<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24a50b2c31781599252dfff67f6089c2829f011","tid":553224,"uid":6752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"中文成績有數據睇係差左<br />\n淨係識拎學生黎玩"}]}